data.description: Freshly painted 3BR, 3BA, 2 car garage Prescott Valley home. Granite counter tops and newer lamintate flooring. Master bedroom on lower level. Great location on the east side of town. Great Mingus mountain view from the front deck. Hot tub conveys. Roof installed in 2016 with transferable warranty. New water heater in 2022. Huge side yard could be used for terraced landscape or vegetable gardens.
